+{\footnote index:00007}
K{\footnote ;Creation of hint collections;Userdefined files;Development;THL files;}
{\f5\fs48\cf2\li120\ri250\sb40\sa40\b\ql Creating your own THL files}\par\pard
{\f0\fs20\cf1\li180\ri250\sb20\sa60\brdrt}\par\pard
{\f2\fs20\cf1\li180\ri250\sb20\sa60\ql If you wish to design and spread own hint collections, please pay attention to the following advices:}\par\pard
{\f0\cf1\li180\ri250\sa-260\fs16\fi0}\par\pard
{\f0\brdrth\box\fs20\cf1\li180\ri250\sb20\sa60\f4 \'B7\f0\brdrth\box\fs20\cf1\li180\ri250\sb20\sa60\ql\li540\fi-360\tx540\tab Before starting your work you should contact me to check if anyone else is working on a file about your topic. This is done to avoid double works on one topic and to make it possible to me to keep an eye on the progress of the THL project.}\par\pard
{\f0\brdrth\box\fs20\cf1\li180\ri250\sb20\sa60\f4 \'B7\f0\brdrth\box\fs20\cf1\li180\ri250\sb20\sa60\ql\li540\fi-360\tx540\tab Think about the structure of your hint collection. Where can questions occur ? When is picture support usefull ? Which logical parts can be defined ?}\par\pard
{\f0\brdrth\box\fs20\cf1\li180\ri250\sb20\sa60\f4 \'B7\f0\brdrth\box\fs20\cf1\li180\ri250\sb20\sa60\ql\li540\fi-360\tx540\tab Compare your solution with different solutions to prevent errors or omissions.}\par\pard
{\f0\brdrth\box\fs20\cf1\li180\ri250\sb20\sa60\f4 \'B7\f0\brdrth\box\fs20\cf1\li180\ri250\sb20\sa60\ql\li540\fi-360\tx540\tab Please make sure not to violate any copyrights. Ordinarily it is prohibited to transform commercial hint books into electronical systems. If you have doubt about legimitation please contact the author of the original.}\par\pard
{\f0\brdrth\box\fs20\cf1\li180\ri250\sb20\sa60\f4 \'B7\f0\brdrth\box\fs20\cf1\li180\ri250\sb20\sa60\ql\li540\fi-360\tx540\tab You should spread THL files only. Remember that anyone is able to edit the data in a THR file, but always keep a copy of your THR file at a secure place. A THL file can not be edited with the THL {\uldb editor}{\v Der_Editor}.}\par\pard
{\f0\brdrth\box\fs20\cf1\li180\ri250\sb20\sa60\f4 \'B7\f0\brdrth\box\fs20\cf1\li180\ri250\sb20\sa60\ql\li540\fi-360\tx540\tab Please send a copy of your THL file to me. The easiest way to do is uploading the file to the following ftp-site:\line \b ftp://members.aol.com/thlhome/incoming\b0 \line Alternativly you can send the file by mail or name a internet site where I can download the file.}\par\pard
